  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/webkit\/domdocument-additions\ncrawled: 2025-12-12T01:25:01Z\n---\n\n# DOMDocument Additions\n\n**API Collection**\n\nAdditions to the `DOMDocument` class facilitate communication between the DOM API and WebKit and help convert DOM URL element attributes into web-friendly URLs.\n\n## Getting the web frame\n\n- **webFrame**: The web frame associated with the DOM document.\n\n## Constructing URLs\n\n- **url(withAttributeString:)**: Constructs a URL given an attribute string.\n\n## Related Documentation\n\n- **WebKit DOM Programming Topics**\n- **WebKit Objective-C Programming Guide**\n\n## Document Object Model (DOM) APIs\n\n- **DOMAbstractView**\n- **DOMAttr**\n- **DOMBlob**\n- **DOMCDATASection**\n- **DOMCharacterData**\n- **DOMComment**\n- **DOMCounter**\n- **DOMCSSCharsetRule**\n- **DOMCSSFontFaceRule**\n- **DOMCSSImportRule**\n- **DOMCSSMediaRule**\n- **DOMCSSPageRule**\n- **DOMCSSPrimitiveValue**\n- **DOMCSSRule**\n- **DOMCSSRuleList**\n\n",
